{"tid":293320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"80蚊一個鐘請人","createTime":"2017-06-22T05:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T07:58:00.000Z","uid":48881,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92716c299baee3f6e0ff4c5f438d494c0ed2f1af","tid":293320,"uid":48881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"地點:將軍澳 工業區 食物工場<br />\n<br />\n時間:1400-2300(9小時)<br />\n人工:一個月大約返20-24日到每日9小時(80x9=720x20 日=14400)萬4-萬6左右，星期六日多數放假，<br />\n<br />\n食飯時間:半小時，要帶飯，有蒸櫃，雪櫃，微波爐，冷熱水機<br />\n<br />\n工作內容:搬材料，倒料，出料，頭2小時辛苦d，跟住大約每做20分鐘有得坐5-7分鐘，睇你速度，<br />\n材料大約15kg重，有車仔推有電牌用，好易上手。<br />\n<br />\n工場入面:唔比用手機,有制服，鞋提供<br />\n<br />\n頭幾日有人帶住做，係遠d，我做左2個月，幾好做<br />\n交通:返工:坑口站有公司車直到，放工:公司車到坑口站，觀唐，鑽石山<br />\n<br />\n要男工，有氣有力<br />\n有興趣就係tg留言，我今日番緊工14-23，要食飯或者今晚12點先可以回覆<br />\ntg:@poolo2046"},{"pid":"3e8950f8443f216ec526d897614bb7804d8b1a3e","tid":293320,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:38:57.000Z","msg":"食飯先得30分鐘"},{"pid":"6fe2e281f24e8e08e207062c54dbc94b03656767","tid":293320,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁快升職做判頭"},{"pid":"dea0bc626823aa6417cff955771513e624864864","tid":293320,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"半個鐘食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線"},{"pid":"b0d3098f54a69ad847d751f3ffed41779ccca2b7","tid":293320,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"淨係唔俾用手機呢樣，至少150蚊一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c425c79c7d0c0016f1b2568512d2189154ff958f","tid":293320,"uid":66360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半個鐘食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n之前番美心工廠都係半個鐘食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d637083df2139ce740dbc0530d510ad309177e81","tid":293320,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:13:53.000Z","msg":"其實算唔錯嘅<br />\n除咗無得用電話<br />\n係咪連跟身都唔俾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過應該辛苦到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係點會80蚊都要上嚟請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b31c1049b654a058e0573995de527be741ef75","tid":293320,"uid":83618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:17:21.000Z","msg":"80一個鐘，睇怕搬既都唔輕，仲要手機都無得用，<br />\n地盤上料一工最小都900-1000，工時無咁長食飯無咁短，唔係等住開飯都好難有人做"},{"pid":"45285181266876a7eaa65e83ff8be83b30721be0","tid":293320,"uid":43033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"冇得用電話 200起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3510b2dbf1eb55a719901c4f6f32f2fcd9fbdf70","tid":293320,"uid":48881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"唔會好辛苦，每次搬5箱野，15kg洛車仔，做2次，有得坐5-7分鐘"},{"pid":"0273104703fb36545bcb600e9ff377fd24fdbef8","tid":293320,"uid":118710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁快升職做判頭</blockquote>員工介紹人做有錢個D呀"}]}